# Seanime Extensions

A collection of plugins that extend the functionality of Seanime.

## Plugins

### AniList Integration

- **Anilist Autopause** - Automatically set media status to `PAUSED` after a set period of time
- **Anilist Favorites** - Manage and display your favorite anime/manga/characters/staffs/studios
- **Anilist Forums** - Browse AniList forums
- **Anilist Notes** - Add personal notes to anime/manga entries
- **Anilist Private** - Manage anime/manga list visibility
- **Anilist Watch Order** - Display optimal watch order for franchises

### Sync Services

- **MyAnimeListSync** - Synchronize with [MyAnimeList](https://myanimelist.net)
- **KitsuSync** - Synchronize with [Kitsu](https://kitsu.io)
- **ShikimoriSync** - Synchronize with [Shikimori](https://shikimori.one)
- **SimklSync** - Synchronize with [Simkl](https://simkl.com)
- **TraktSync** - Synchronize with [Trakt](https://trakt.tv)

### List Management

- **Alternative Titles** - Display alternative anime titles
- **Custom Episode Metadata** - Add custom metadata to episodes
- **Untracked** - Disable tracking for selected anime

### Customization

- **Custom CSS Manager** - Manage custom CSS styles
- **Discord RPC Hide NSFW** - Hide NSFW status in Discord RPC
- **Fancy Fonts** - Apply fancy fonts to the interface

### Utilities

- **Notes** - Personal note management
- **Vault** - Local media collection management

## Installation

Go to Seanime in-app marketplace and install these plugins directly.

## Contributing

Each plugin folder contains:

- `provider.ts` - Main plugin implementation
- `[plugin-name].json` - Plugin metadata and configuration
- `.d.ts` - TypeScript type definitions (where applicable)
